data.description_suggestion: Retrieves daily performance metrics time series data for a business location across a specified date range. Example request: `GET https://businessprofileperformance.googleapis.com/v1/locations/12345/searchkeywords/impressions/monthly?monthly_range.start_month.year=2022&monthly_range.start_month.month=1&monthly_range.end_month.year=2022&monthly_range.end_month.month=3`
data.description_suggestion: Retrieves search keywords and their monthly impression counts for a business location. Returns a ListSearchKeywordImpressionsMonthlyResponse containing SearchKeywordCount objects, each with a keyword and its aggregated monthly impression data. Requires a valid location resource name and a monthly date range (start_month and end_month). Impressions are aggregated across Google Search and Google Maps for the specified period.
